Is not it?

When will I become an adult?

What?
Is that strange?
Not really.
See?
Crap!
Shit...

Yeah!

Brother...

Yeah.
I know.
Are you all right?
Your stomach ache?

Nothing.
What do you mean?
Weirdo.
